In [9]:
x , y = image_in_frequency.shape
Laplacian_filter = np.zeros((x , y) , dtype=np.float32)
for i in range(x):
    for j in range(y):
        Laplacian_filter[i,j] = -4*np.pi*np.pi*((i-x/2)**2 + (j-y/2)**2)
In [10]:
plt.subplot(1,1,1)
plt.imshow(Laplacian_filter , cmap = 'gray')
plt.title('Laplacian filter')
plt.xticks([])
plt.yticks([])
plt.show()
In [11]:
Laplacian_image = Laplacian_filter * image_in_frequency
In [12]:
Laplacian_image = np.fft.ifftshift(Laplacian_image)
In [13]:
Laplacian_image = np.real(np.fft.ifft2(Laplacian_image))
In [14]:
oldrange = np.max(Laplacian_image) - np.min(Laplacian_image)
In [15]:
newrange = 1 - (-1)
In [16]:
Laplacian_image_in_new_range = (((Laplacian_image - np.min(Laplacian_image)) * newrange) / oldrange ) + -1
In [17]:
plt.subplot(1,1,1)

plt.axis('off')
plt.title('Laplacian image')
plt.show()
In [18]:
c = -1
